      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for a daily driver, backup car, or project. It shows its age and wear, but presents a solid value opportunity for the right buyer who wants straightforward transportation without a big price tag. A practical choice for someone who appreciates honest condition and room to make it their own.",
