    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right owner? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option for someone who needs basic wheels, a starter project, or a handy backup vehicle. It has character, a comfortable feel on the road, and the kind of value that\u2019s getting harder to find. If you\u2019re realistic and want something inexpensive with potential, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 5900.0,
