      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with strong driver/project potential. It shows its age cosmetically and is being sold in poor overall condition, but the drivetrain still offers usable performance and the chassis feels like a good foundation for someone who knows their way around basic maintenance. A practical option for a cheap commuter, parts car, or weekend revival candidate. If you want an affordable entry point and don\u2019t mind putting in some work, this one has real value.",
